name: Endless Paretano
description:
Here is a game I made in one night just for fun.

Keeping your car alive means avoiding obstacles. 

PS. You can also destroy the cones with bullets, but you only have three of them, so use them carefully.

PSS. If you don't know the meaning of the word "Paretano" don't be ashamed. Is a ""italian"" word used to indicate the habitants of an italian city, where this type of acts are really common.
